{"tid":1631501,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[未FC]FB傳 CSD職員\"蘇花老公\"已經被炒...","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T01:49:33.000Z","uid":195084,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9de44cd99c5af052d724777d10d57fe28ee9d0","tid":1631501,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gbmW9e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgbmW9e2.png&h=0d1e6a62&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nFrom Facebook page : 全球監察［林鄭月娥］行政長官官方群組<br />\n睇落似係真<br />\n唉 雖然唔知你會唔會見到<br />\n但多謝巴打你對呢場運動既貢獻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今場運動贏左之後一定會爭取幫你復職<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見無人提起所以想開Post 多謝下巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋以後各位如果想貼職員證 麻煩你一定要遮哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好畀班狗高層捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56ea38ed7f1137e21c74fe9f7aeac0618221d80","tid":1631501,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81281cb3d044bfce1c53def3cdaa8a9945b3eef","tid":1631501,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打"},{"pid":"ac857d5bee84d9d9a903724cdfaf90c08307b8d4","tid":1631501,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb344bd68a5c517aeb49f1bc4d1526972824553b","tid":1631501,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7666fcdb8b795d0971ac3507d6026fbc9b58ad4a","tid":1631501,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"原來講撚錯<br />\n係一定會復職<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e93566eb061f44483f051ffc6ab1730a160767a","tid":1631501,"uid":296789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"蘇花老公可唔可以上黎報個平安 好擔心<br />\n不過我頭先去睇返個post果1001個reply<br />\n已經見到邊個係兇手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇連登仔可以起返條友底呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f075d9cd4f76da58e989d0dd331b16ed18e1a824","tid":1631501,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi